  "title": "All-Party Parliamentary Group on Counter Extremism",
  "purpose": "This group will tackle rising extremism below the terrorism threshold, including online hate, disinformation, and community intimidation. It aims to raise awareness, promote evidence-based solutions, and protect the UK’s democratic values and social cohesion.",
